{"tid":915550,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"IOS 終於可以自製WhatsApp Stickers！","createTime":"2018-11-25T05:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T05:36:45.000Z","uid":223797,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a0a138d8448df5c3fce4584f3ff11f493778b5a2","tid":915550,"uid":223797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T05:26:52.000Z","msg":"如題，小弟不才，應朋友訴求上星期整左隻 iOS app 幫大家可以自製WhatsApp Sticker<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身想等我第二個bug fix version 出到街先同大家講。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但PK 蘋果唔批我個新 version ，話咩大多同類型app 又話要依賴其他app 先得咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(DKLM sticker 緊係要WhatsApp 先用到，佢都on99999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n依家個app隨時有機會俾人落架，大家想自製whatsapp sticker就down 左先<br />\n(down 左既app 蘋果落我架都影響唔到你用)<br />\n<br />\nMyStickers:<br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/mystickers/id1442605866?ls=1&amp;mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fmystickers%2Fid1442605866%3Fls%3D1%26mt%3D8&d=tKJvl9cJ4JGxj2E%2F8UpRZG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=d0e0a78f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/mystickers/id1442605866?ls=1&amp;mt=8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/25/132639_2d5972534efb4dfcbba906495c6b978b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F25%2F132639_2d5972534efb4dfcbba906495c6b978b.png&h=95724ba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/25/132641_6b23d53659b4761ce6c0cf0b4ae4d84c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F25%2F132641_6b23d53659b4761ce6c0cf0b4ae4d84c.png&h=ab3e590b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個version 有bug ：<br />\n- 入唔齊name 同 icon 圖會彈app<br />\n- 入太多太大既圖會爆memory 彈app<br />\n- 圖 file size 大過 100KB 會用jpeg 壓縮冇左透明底<br />\n<br />\n祝大家自製到sticker 唔洗俾android fd 屌打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b81b73015e4c36fc91002acfecf13254ffe0a6fd","tid":915550,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T05:36:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}